OL,3,CPolice 'spying' report short on all
OL,4,Cassurances: Policing Board
OL,6,FThe Policing Board has said a report
OL,7,Finto the PSNI's use of covert powers
OL,8,Fin relation to journalists and lawyers
OL,9,Fbrings transparency, but does not
OL,10,Fprovide all the assurance it needs.
OL,12,FThere have been calls for a public
OL,13,Finquiry after the publication of the
OL,14,FPSNI's own report on claims of spying
OL,15,Fon journalists.
OL,17,FPolice in Northern Ireland made 323
OL,18,Fapplications for communications data
OL,19,Frelating to journalists since 2011,
OL,20,Fthe report revealed.
