OL,3,CPolice 'spying' report short on all
OL,4,Cassurances: Policing Board
OL,6,FThe report produced by the PSNI said
OL,7,Fthe vast majority of applications were
OL,8,Frelated to journalists who were
OL,9,Fvictims, suspects or witnesses to
OL,10,Fcrime.
OL,12,FThe report, which was compiled for the
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland Policing Board ` the
OL,14,FPSNI's oversight body, said of the 323
OL,15,Fapplications, 10 sought to identify a
OL,16,Fjournalistic source using covert
OL,17,Fpowers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
