OL,4,Cassurances: Policing Board
OL,6,FThe Policing Board meeting was held in
OL,7,Fprivate session. The board said this
OL,8,Fwas due to the election.
OL,10,FThe National Union of Journalists held
OL,11,Fthe protest before the meeting.
OL,13,FThis week, PSNI Chief Constable Jon
OL,14,FBoutcher announced an independent
OL,15,Freview, headed by Angus McCullough KC,
OL,16,Fof any use of surveillance against
OL,17,Fjournalists and other specific groups
OL,18,Fby the PSNI.
