OL,3,CPolice 'spying' report short on all
OL,4,Cassurances: Policing Board
OL,6,FIt came after concerns were raised
OL,7,Fduring an Investigatory Powers
OL,8,FTribunal (IPT) hearing in London.
OL,10,FThe hearing was during an ongoing case
OL,11,Fexamining allegations that
OL,12,Finvestigative reporters Barry
OL,13,FMcCaffrey and Trevor Birney were
OL,14,Fsubject to unlawful covert
OL,15,Fintelligence by the police.
OL,17,FIt also heard claims the PSNI
OL,18,Fsubjected other journalists to routine
OL,19,Fphone surveillance.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
