OL,3,CPolice 'spying' report short on all
OL,4,Cassurances: Policing Board
OL,6,FMr Boutcher has said much of the
OL,7,Fpublic concern has arisen because of
OL,8,F"misinterpretation of documents" made
OL,9,Favailable in redacted form at the
OL,10,Ftribunal.
OL,12,FAt the Stormont Assembly on Monday,
OL,13,FJustice Minister Naomi Long rejected a
OL,14,Fcall to hold an independent inquiry,
OL,15,Fpointing out it was an issue for the
OL,16,FPolicing Board, the PSNI's oversight
OL,17,Fbody, in the first instance.
OL,19,FHowever, she said she was concerned at
OL,20,Fthe allegations and would act if
OL,21,Fnecessary.
