OL,6,FMr McCaffrey was at the protest
OL,7,Foutside the headquarters of the
OL,8,FPolicing Board.
OL,10,FHe said the review established by Mr
OL,11,FBoutcher did not go far enough because
OL,12,Fit does not have the power to compel
OL,13,Fformer officers to provide information.
OL,15,FHe added: "Only a public inquiry can
OL,16,Fcompel former officers to come and
OL,17,Ftell what they knew.
OL,26,@wD@KOU
