OL,3,CPolice 'spying' report short on all
OL,4,Cassurances: Policing Board
OL,6,F"Somebody in authority within the PSNI
OL,7,Fauthorised and allowed this to happen.
OL,8,FThe public needs to know who allowed
OL,9,Fit to happen.
OL,11,F"There needs to be a public inquiry
OL,12,Fbecause these former police officers
OL,13,Fneed to be compelled to come and give
OL,14,Fevidence.
OL,16,F"Society needs to know what has been
OL,17,Fgoing on for 20 years."
OL,19,FPatrick Corrigan, Northern Ireland
OL,20,Fprogramme director at Amnesty
OL,21,FInternational, was also at the protest.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUyD@WO]
