OL,6,FHe said: "Serious revelations have
OL,7,Fcome out via the Investigatory Powers
OL,8,FTribunal about police spying on
OL,9,Fjournalists and potentially on lawyers
OL,10,Fand others.
OL,12,F"It is the Policing Board's statutory
OL,13,Frole to hold the police accountable so
OL,14,Fwe are asking them to hold an
OL,15,Findependent inquiry into this
OL,16,Fsurveillance scandal and to finally
OL,17,Flay bare what exactly has been going
OL,18,Fon."
OL,20,FThursday's meeting of the Policing
OL,21,FBoard was closed to the media.
